data.title: Why is Paris so ugly?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 30): I can understand how one would say that.

Looking at the facts, Paris ranks among the worst major European cities when it comes to the amount of green spaces, parks per capita: although there are beautiful parks and avenues, they are few and far between.
